* Indescribable instant

37:55.707 --> 37:56.942
* Your heart

37:56.975 --> 37:59.945
* Will speak the truth

37:59.978 --> 38:01.413
* 'Cause in that

38:01.447 --> 38:03.615
* One indescribable

38:03.649 --> 38:05.817
* Magical, mystical

38:05.851 --> 38:07.953
* Endless, incredible

