* Instant

38:10.456 --> 38:11.890
* The only words

38:11.923 --> 38:14.860
* You'll need are

38:14.893 --> 38:18.664
* "I love you"

38:23.635 --> 38:25.637
*

38:44.490 --> 38:46.625
Come with me.

38:57.068 --> 38:59.070
It's over.

38:59.104 --> 39:00.606
What?

39:00.639 --> 39:02.941
Rebecca, Valencia
and I are done.

39:05.777 --> 39:08.814
Becks, I have tried
not to think about you.

39:08.847 --> 39:10.516
I have.

39:10.549 --> 39:12.651
You have no idea
how hard I've tried.

39:12.684 --> 39:14.386
Just, no matter
what I do...

39:15.987 --> 39:17.689
I feel you with me.

39:21.126 --> 39:23.629
(gasps)

39:23.662 --> 39:27.165
Oh, my God,
it's my letter from camp.

39:27.198 --> 39:29.901
You keep this with you,
like, all the time?

39:29.935 --> 39:32.571
Look, I know
you're with Greg, but...

39:32.604 --> 39:34.606
Stop.

39:41.847 --> 39:44.115
* In one indescribable

39:44.149 --> 39:47.085
* Instant

39:47.118 --> 39:49.087
* There is no time

39:49.120 --> 39:51.590
* Or space

39:51.623 --> 39:54.993
* In one indescribable

39:55.026 --> 39:56.828
* Instant

39:56.862 --> 40:00.799
* It all falls into place

40:00.832 --> 40:04.536
* In one indescribable

40:04.570 --> 40:05.871
* Instant

40:05.904 --> 40:07.739
* Your dreams

40:07.773 --> 40:10.709
* Will all come true

40:10.742 --> 40:12.444
* 'Cause in that

40:12.478 --> 40:14.813
* One indescribable

40:14.846 --> 40:16.815
* Magical, mystical

40:16.848 --> 40:19.485
* Endless, incredible

40:19.518 --> 40:20.752
* Barely believable

40:20.786 --> 40:23.822
* Truly unlikely

40:23.855 --> 40:26.992
* But not inconceivable

40:27.025 --> 40:29.628
* What, are you kidding me

40:29.661 --> 40:31.897
* No, it's for realable

40:31.930 --> 40:35.701
* Instant

40:35.734 --> 40:38.837
* The only words

40:38.870 --> 40:40.906
* You'll need are

40:40.939 --> 40:44.843
* "I love

40:44.876 --> 40:49.881
* You..."

40:58.924 --> 41:02.160
(song ends)

41:02.193 --> 41:05.030
I love you, Rebecca.

41:05.063 --> 41:08.667
I should have said "I love you."

41:08.700 --> 41:10.636
(retches, coughs)

41:18.309 --> 41:20.278
Hey, Josh?

41:20.311 --> 41:22.280
(short chuckle)
Yeah, Becks?

41:22.313 --> 41:24.282
Can I tell you something?

41:24.315 --> 41:26.518
Yeah.

41:27.686 --> 41:30.021
I moved here for you.

41:30.055 --> 41:32.891
What?

41:32.924 --> 41:36.695
The second I saw you on
the street in New York, I knew.

41:36.728 --> 41:40.165
I j-- I just knew you were
the answer to all my problems.

41:40.198 --> 41:42.901
And I lost sight
of it for a minute,

41:42.934 --> 41:45.771
but now I know for sure.

41:45.804 --> 41:47.773
Mmm.

41:47.806 --> 41:50.008
This is our moment, Josh Chan.

41:51.943 --> 41:55.581
I'm so excited that our
love story can finally begin.

